{"tid":1673872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭斯表明美國「與港並肩」, 但暗示和平示威先方便佢哋做嘢","createTime":"2019-10-25T01:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T16:48:28.000Z","uid":325827,"like":9,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"35ecebedbc766872ce199cc5a1366740bd24ef37","tid":1673872,"uid":325827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:47:46.000Z","msg":"【抗暴之戰】彭斯演說表明美「與港並肩」 轟NBA向華跪低儼如中國附屬公司<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191025/60190008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191025%2F60190008&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=3841e20b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191025%2F60190008&h=96804709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191025/60190008</a><br />\n<br />\n彭斯指，香港本可成為中國展示擁抱自由一面的活榜樣，可惜中國近年加強對香港的干預，限制香港人的權利與自由。彭斯表示，數百萬港人走上街頭和平抗議，美國也站出來為港人發聲，總統特朗普也明確表示必須人道處理，呼籲中國尊重1984年《中英聯合聲明》。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他說美國樂見港府已撤回引發示威的《逃犯條例》，而北京亦表現克制。他向港人表示，「與你們並肩，我們受你們啟發」，呼籲香港人繼續以非暴力方式抗爭。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab4e45b7cf9520cf61266bd00de02ee39baff37","tid":1673872,"uid":14918,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:49:14.000Z","msg":"你個title第二句係咪加左你個人見解?"},{"pid":"200c45ad3482e25e9d4693f03219783d5e1a7411","tid":1673872,"uid":108337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:50:11.000Z","msg":"On9 misleading"},{"pid":"93a30affef100f3757c8d28129ab2e418a233556","tid":1673872,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:52:09.000Z","msg":"但係佢都話到而家為止都仲係和平示威<br />\n唔似琴晚英國上議院部分人咁話香港要停止暴力先開始到政改<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hk